  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nNA - cannot run\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\nfoundryup\n\n### Operating System\n\nLinux\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nI have seen this issue a few times in the past on this repo however most of the fixes that I have seen are to use `ubuntu-latest` instead of a specific version. I have tried both and am getting the same issue however I am not calling this directly within a github action.\r\n\r\nI am using cross-rs to have both x86 and arm64 builds on linux to be deployed to dockerhhub.\r\n\r\nHere are the relevant files that are causing the issues.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/alchemyplatform/rundler/blob/josh/release-pipeline/.github/workflows/docker-release.yaml\r\nhttps://github.com/alchemyplatform/rundler/blob/josh/release-pipeline/Cross.toml\r\nhttps://github.com/alchemyplatform/rundler/blob/josh/release-pipeline/Makefile\r\n\r\nWe use forge in a build.rs file in the rundler project for autogenerated bindings to solidity which is why it needs to be in the image and not just in the actions runtime \r\n\r\n```\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libm.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.27' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libm.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.29' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.29' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.25' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.28' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 /root/.foundry/bin/forge: /lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/libc.so.6: version `GLIBC_2.27' not found (required by /root/.foundry/bin/forge)\r\n#5 11.59 foundryup: command failed: /root/.foundry/bin/forge --version\r\n#5 11.59 foundryup: installed - \r\n\r\n```",
